WEBVTT

00:00.845 --> 00:03.419
Summer travel is more popular than ever...

00:03.683 --> 00:06.448
...and this list of our top locations might help you...

00:06.543 --> 00:09.189
...get a head start on your summer preparations.

00:10.743 --> 00:15.364
A summer trip to Tanzania will allow you to experience the safari season.

00:16.547 --> 00:21.829
Tanzania defies categorization as the site of memorable Serengeti safaris...

00:21.942 --> 00:25.928
...and tranquil immersion on Zanzibar's soft sand beaches,...

00:26.241 --> 00:31.981
...offering insights into unique animals, vibrant birds and remarkable culture.

00:33.359 --> 00:36.322
Cuban summers are authentic and vibrant.

00:37.300 --> 00:43.493
The island is enveloped in tropical warmth punctuated by atmospheric seasonal rains...

00:43.584 --> 00:48.466
...that assist to calm the days or create a sensuous soundtrack to the evening.

00:49.655 --> 00:51.428
From Havana to Santiago,...

00:51.768 --> 00:57.678
...the seasonal heat only fuels local fervor as music, art and a sense of community...

00:57.828 --> 00:59.705
...erupt around every corner.

01:00.666 --> 01:06.723
The remaining colonial architecture seeps with history and tradition shapes current culture.

01:07.760 --> 01:11.646
Cuba is an intriguing summer getaway with its coral reefs,...

01:11.945 --> 01:15.746
...gorgeous shoreline and a society eager  to enjoy.

